    <stitle>ELECTRICAL SYSTEM TROUBLESHOOTING GUIDE - 5000i and 9000i - SLEEPER LIGHTING AND ACCESSORIES - DESCRIPTION -
        Power Source (Sleeper)
    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="describe" graphiccount="0">
        <title>Power Source (Sleeper)</title>
        <para>Two power sources (power socket) are provided to enable 12 volt accessories to be plugged in. A socket is
            located near the base of the bunk coming out of the right bulkhead auxiliary power (luggage compartment)
            behind the passenger seat and another socket is located in the control panel auxiliary power source.
        </para>
